schools.name: Charles J. Colgan Sr. High School

data.description: Exceptional end unit townhome located in the highly desirable REIDS PROSPECT, boasting 3 bedrooms and 2 full and 2 half baths. Revel in the elegance of wood floors, as the foyer unfolds into a spacious recreation room. Step outside to a charming brick patio overlooking a meticulously landscaped backyard, complete with the added benefits of a French drain and sprinkler system for peace of mind and convenience. The main level showcases an inviting open floor plan, perfect for both relaxed living and entertaining. The gourmet eat-in kitchen is a highlight with custom stainless steel countertop island, tons of cabinets and the living room is adorned with custom shelves. Enjoy moments of relaxation or host gatherings on the Trex deck, featuring automatic lights and scenic views of mature trees. Ascend upstairs to discover the luxurious Primary suite, offering a vaulted ceiling, a cozy sitting area, a sizable walk-in closet with custom built shelves, and a master bath with a tub, shower, and double sinks. Two additional generously sized bedrooms and a full bath round out the upper level, completing this stunning townhome. The hardwood entry foyer offers custom shelves for shoes/coats. HVAC (2019), Sprinkler System (2022)**location is perfect with 35 minutes to Dulles & Reagan airports, 10 minutes or so to Stonebridge(Wegmans/Apple/upscale retail), Potomac Mills, HOV ride share, VRE (VA Rail express), several Parks & Potomac River.  Fantastic schools including Colgan High School (constructed a few years ago for $112M)***Basement has custom built shelves, organizers, countertops along with extra working area in Laundry room to assist former home based baking business***THIS HOME IS GORGEOUS!!!***
